name: Nyla (purp.alpaca)
description:
My third Textual Inversion embedding!
Download the file and place it in the stable-diffusion-webui\embeddings folder.

The previews are done in a lot of different models to show that it works in more than one. :)

Add bs_purpalpaca in your prompt to use her.

Trained on SD 1.5 so will only work with 1.5 models.

Shout out to https://civitai.com/user/dddokter for helping me test her!
